WHAT IS IT?
-----------

  'Gemology' is a Workbench game where you try to place gems of
the same type together either horizontally or vertically. Between
3 to 8 types of gems are randomly placed on the 8 by 8 board. Try
to remove all gems from each game board.

  Have fun!

FEATURES
--------

-Simple installation: just run the game and play!

-Many game patterns to play with.

-Small package, the Lha archive is smaller than 50K, so it doesn't
 take ages to download :)

-The game plays on the Workbench screen and its window is
 resizeable.

